[[File:Cityguard_house_256.png|right]]
The '''City Guard House''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It allows recruitment of City Guards and, if upgraded, increases their recruitment speed. Placing a [[Barracks]] beside a City Guard House will NOT increase recruitment speed.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 3

